title: 2: Flying Across the Country to get Cheated On
description: A never told story that has been sitting on Sadies chest since New Years Eve is finally being told. Over a year long of a secret long distance “relationship” that ended up being thrown in a blender and chopped up is finally being told by Sadie herself … buckle up people.
